09/11/2008
ATHENS, Greece -- The Greek parliament on Friday (November 7th) adopted a bill to ban public smoking starting January 1st 2010 in compliance with the EU's guidelines against secondhand smoke. The measure will apply to all restaurants, bars, offices and public transport. (ANA-MPA, Kathimerini, In.news, SKAI, DPA - 07/11/08) 
